                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">Although this papyrus is in very bad condition, badly damaged and broken off at all sides, it preserves the four margins. It is vertically damaged at the middle of the text, probably as a result of a fold. There is a big part at the right side is lost (mostly was blank); it also has suffered holes, fibers removed and misaligned.</ab>
                        </condition>
